I'm in Kinspite in Wales, which was recently in bloom in the National Botanic Garden and

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:35.120
I went and saw it and it was a bloody ugly thing, huge, massive, monstrous, grey, looked

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:38.720
