00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:44.600
But when it bloomed it was beautiful, it was amazing, it had these lovely golden cups and

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:49.400
they were full of nectar and you can drink them, humans can drink them, animals can drink

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:51.880
them and it kind of gives you a high.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:57.760
So this is a poem about that plant, it's called a Puyya plant, which is kind of a horrible

00:06:57.760 --> 00:06:59.760
name as well for this thing.

00:06:59.760 --> 00:07:05.120
It only blooms every ten years, so that was in April this year and this is a poem for

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:06.120
the Puyya.

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:11.960
Puyya, they call you, the words sticky in their mouths.

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:17.000
You prickle the roof of the glass house and settle the groups of visiting classes.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:20.680
Like a nettle your leaves are sting sharp, laced with thorns.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:25.960
Cruel, they remark, your taste is for animal flesh, which they hook, pull in and starve

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:26.960
to death.

00:07:27.160 --> 00:07:31.960
Their blood is your food, your bed more wet with this than dew.

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:37.780
From the Andes to Llanarthni you came, a monster baby in a way, eight feet tall and closer

00:07:37.780 --> 00:07:39.840
to a mutant than a flower.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:43.040
Towering above the others, a giant in the nursery.

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:49.000
Cursed to slowness, reliant on your new owners, still you grew, your brontosaurus neck too

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:55.000
thick for them to prune, a Chilean imposter that loomed above its human masters.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:59.200
But now, a decade later, you're in bud, about to blossom.

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:02.200
Your body is round and fulsome as a woman's.

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:07.160
Crowds come to marvel, wondering at your beauty, eyes hunger for your form.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:10.560
Cameras snap and looks are thrown, but sweeter than before.

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:13.000
You ignore them, take no note.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:17.000
Your name now sweet as nectar in every thirsting throat.

